Company: Mr. Janitor, Eagle Harbor Country Club
Description of incident: The owner of a cleaning company called "Mr. Janitor" was arrested for stealing personal information from Eagle Harbor Country Club members.  An unknown number of members had their information stolen and used to open fraudulent credit cards and bank accounts in their names.  The owner of the cleaning company was charged with identity theft of more than $50,000 and/or affecting more than twenty persons.
